title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 20 2021

description:
Former NYT journalist Alex Berenson joins Clay and Buck again with his own “See, I Told So” about covid vaccines and masks. What we're seeing in Afghanistan is the people in charge are morons. Retired NFL quarterback Jay Cutler on being canceled for his anti-mask stance in schools, and his bid to become a school board member. Will the Taliban get a seat at the UN? Buck give best man toast advice. Clay hints at his celebrity poker strategy.
